He's made a decision!

253
00:12:39,126 --> 00:12:40,877
His heart belongs to the dojo.

254
00:12:40,877 --> 00:12:45,966
Will you shut up and quit
putting words in my mouth!

255
00:12:45,966 --> 00:12:48,635
Are you guys spying on us!

256
00:12:48,635 --> 00:12:50,304
I can't believe I live
with these people.

257
00:12:50,304 --> 00:12:54,099
Wow, that was kind of scary.
You are absolutely nothing

258
00:12:54,099 --> 00:12:57,477
like the good girl you
pretend to be at school.

259
00:12:57,477 --> 00:12:59,897
Kenichi, weren't you saying
something about training?

260
00:12:59,897 --> 00:13:01,607
You really shouldn't
