261
00:13:01,607 --> 00:13:02,941
Oh! Right.

262
00:13:02,941 --> 00:13:06,445
Izumi, So glad you stopped
by, it's been a pleasure.

263
00:13:06,445 --> 00:13:08,780
You're welcome to stay longer,
but I'm sure all the fighting,

264
