even last two seconds.

276
00:13:31,345 --> 00:13:34,264
Well, we'll just see about that.

277
00:13:34,264 --> 00:13:36,183
I want to take the trial course!

278
00:13:36,183 --> 00:13:40,771
Hey wait a minute, Izumi!
This isn't a regular dojo!

279
00:13:40,771 --> 00:13:44,274
