Then go right ahead.

280
00:13:44,274 --> 00:13:49,404
Just don't act like we
didn't warn you, okay?

281
00:13:49,404 --> 00:13:52,032
Thank you for letting
me try out, Miu.

282
00:13:52,032 --> 00:13:53,200
Uh don't mention it.

283
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:55,994
Is there any particular
style you wanna try first?

284
00:13:55,994 --> 00:13:57,829
What have I gotten myself into?

285
00:13:57,829 --> 00:14:00,290
I've practically begged her
to physically assault me.

286
00:14:00,290 --> 00:14:03,543
This afternoon has seriously
spiraled out of control.

287
00:14:03,543 --> 00:14:08,674
But it was her idea, not mine.

288
00:14:08,674 --> 00:14:10,634
Kenichi's already
itching to intervene.

289
00:14:10,634 --> 00:14:11,885
Man, he sure is predictable.

290
00:14:11,885 --> 00:14:14,137
His biggest weakness is
his uncontrollable urge

291
00:14:14,137 --> 00:14:16,056
