299
00:14:46,002 --> 00:14:49,756
Oh, well, you can either
choose Jujitsu, Judo,

300
00:14:49,756 --> 00:14:51,258
Kung Fu, Muay Thai...

301
00:14:51,258 --> 00:14:53,593
Why don't you pick the person
