302
00:14:53,593 --> 00:14:54,845
Uh, hey, Akisame.

303
00:14:54,845 --> 00:14:57,723
You're a gentle artist,
you should teach her.

304
00:14:57,723 --> 00:14:58,974
Guess what, Apachai?

305
00:14:58,974 --> 00:15:03,311
