you also want to learn?

317
00:15:26,126 --> 00:15:27,043
Well?

318
00:15:27,043 --> 00:15:28,420
Thanks, but I'll pass.

319
00:15:28,420 --> 00:15:30,213
Fine, but there's
nothing more embarrassing

320
00:15:30,213 --> 00:15:33,049
