is not an easy dojo.

327
00:15:46,146 --> 00:15:49,357
Before I accept you, there is
a rigorous entry test to pass.

328
00:15:49,357 --> 00:15:52,527
Oh. Well I guess
that's only fair.

329
00:15:52,527 --> 00:15:54,362
Then you must
complete ten pushups.

330
00:15:54,362 --> 00:15:55,322
What?!

331
00:15:55,322 --> 00:15:57,324
C'mon, Grandpa,
quit joking around!

332
00:15:57,324 --> 00:15:59,493
Will you please give
her a real test?

333
