I forgot to mention you can
only use your left thumb.

334
00:16:03,330 --> 00:16:05,582
That's not fair!
It's not even possible!

335
00:16:05,582 --> 00:16:07,125
Nobody can do that!

336
00:16:07,125 --> 00:16:11,338
Actually, it's very
possible. Just look.

337
00:16:11,338 --> 00:16:15,842
