338
00:16:15,842 --> 00:16:17,260
You've gotta be kidding me!

339
00:16:17,260 --> 00:16:19,179
If you can't even do
this, then your life

340
00:16:19,179 --> 00:16:22,891
will be in serious
danger here. Ten.

341
00:16:22,891 --> 00:16:25,352
I suppose that might
be too difficult

342
00:16:25,352 --> 00:16:29,314
