427
00:21:19,598 --> 00:21:20,390
That's funny.

428
00:21:20,390 --> 00:21:22,351
I got the impression
you wanted he to join.

429
00:21:22,351 --> 00:21:24,228
I think you were showing off.

430
00:21:24,228 --> 00:21:26,230
You obviously had more
energy than usual

431
00:21:26,230 --> 00:21:28,148
and I don't think that
was a coincidence.

432
00:21:28,148 --> 00:21:30,692
C'mon, that's not true.

433
00:21:30,692 --> 00:21:32,486
Really? That's what
it looked like.

434
00:21:32,486 --> 00:21:35,030
By the way, Kenichi,
how many pushups

435
00:21:35,030 --> 00:21:37,658
can you do with your thumb?

436
00:21:37,658 --> 00:21:39,660
I'll be shocked
if he can do ten.

437
00:21:39,660 --> 00:21:41,662
I'm sure he can
at least do 20.

438
00:21:41,662 --> 00:21:43,747
Well, for Miu it was
a piece of cake.

439
00:21:43,747 --> 00:21:45,540
Apa, Apa!

440
00:21:45,540 --> 00:21:47,626
Don't make me!

441
00:21:47,626 --> 00:21:49,544
So? How many?

442
00:21:56,134 --> 00:21:58,178
It seemed like such a perfect
plan, but there were just

443
00:21:58,178 --> 00:22:00,055
