elements involved.

444
00:22:00,055 --> 00:22:02,766
It's too bad, but I guess
we'll have to call it a day.

445
00:22:02,766 --> 00:22:04,851
Just as long as I've got
Kenichi on my side,

446
00:22:04,851 --> 00:22:07,396
I don't need to worry about
my grand plans for the future.

447
00:22:07,396 --> 00:22:08,647
And today wasn't a total bust.

448
00:22:08,647 --> 00:22:11,942
